  <p>The union <span><a href="d77326bf-8ed7-4e1d-9429-965c2cd97f37" data-linktype="relative-path">ExecEnvDataEx</a></span> has
  the <span><a href="b4295b0e-c641-40ab-bbdb-ea44323b0804" data-linktype="relative-path">EXECENVDATAEX_LEVEL1</a></span>
  structure.</p>
  </td>
 </tr></tbody></table>
</dd></dl><p><b>Data:</b>  Contains information at a
specified level of detail about sessions running on a computer. This is of type
ExecEnvDataEx.</p></div>